<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color:black;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #0033a0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-us {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Section Style */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* How It Works Section */
        .system-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .step {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            flex: 1 1 200px;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

            .step img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 8px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

            .step h3 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
                color: #0033a0;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

        /* Mission Section */
        .mission-points {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .mission-point {
            background-color: #e6f7ff;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .mission-point h3 {
                color: #0033a0;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .mission-point p {
                color: #555;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-us">
        <!-- About Us Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
                Welcome to the Passport Generation System. We are dedicated to making the passport application process easy, secure, and accessible for everyone.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- About Passports Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Passports</h2>
            <p>
                A passport is a vital document for international travel. It serves as proof of identity and nationality, ensuring you can cross borders, access consular assistance, and explore the world. Our system ensures a hassle-free process for obtaining this essential document.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- How It Works Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>How Our System Works</h2>
            <div class="system-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <img src="~/img/create.webp" alt="User Registration">
                    <h3>1. Register</h3>
                    <p>Sign up on our platform with your personal details to create an account.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <img src="~/img/1.jpeg" alt="Apply for Passport">
                    <h3>2. Apply</h3>
                    <p>Fill out the online application form, upload required documents, and pay the fee securely.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <img src="~/img/44.webp" alt="Track Application">
                    <h3>3. Track</h3>
                    <p>Use our system to track your application status in real-time from submission to approval.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <img src="~/img/aa.webp" alt="Passport Delivery">
                    <h3>4. Receive</h3>
                    <p>Once approved, your passport will be delivered to your address or ready for collection.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Mission Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <div class="mission-points">
                <div class="mission-point">
                    <h3>1. Simplify the Process</h3>
                    <p>We aim to make passport applications straightforward and accessible to everyone with an easy-to-use platform.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-point">
                    <h3>2. Ensure Security</h3>
                    <p>We prioritize the security of your personal and payment information, ensuring a safe application experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-point">
                    <h3>3. Provide Real-Time Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Our system allows users to track their application progress, providing updates every step of the way.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-point">
                    <h3>4. Deliver Fast Service</h3>
                    <p>We strive to process and deliver passports as quickly as possible, ensuring a smooth and timely experience for our users.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
